## Focus Area Prioritisation

Always end with exactly **3 focus areas**. Rank by this priority stack (highest first):

1. **Active blockers** â€” anything blocking a squad member right now
2. **Sprint boundary urgency** â€” sprint ends within 3 days, stories at risk of not completing
3. **Reporting deadlines** â€” status reports, steering committee prep, exec updates due this week
4. **Pending decisions** â€” decisions only the PM can make that are holding up work
5. **Strategic work** â€” OKR progress, roadmap updates, stakeholder alignment

Each focus area must be specific and actionable (not &quot;check on sprint&quot; but &quot;Unblock CORTEX-1234: Justin needs access to EDB staging â€” escalate to Sasi&quot;).

