### Step 6 â€” Calculate Financial Metrics

For each option, calculate:

- **Net Present Value (NPV)** â€” 3-year horizon, using Westpac standard discount rate.
- **Return on Investment (ROI)** â€” (Total Benefits - Total Costs) / Total Costs Ã— 100.
- **Payback Period** â€” month/quarter when cumulative benefits exceed cumulative costs.
- **Cost-Benefit Ratio** â€” Total Benefits / Total Costs.

