&gt; **Action Required**: [Team/Person] â€” [specific action] by [DD-MMM-YYYY].

### FYI / No Action

Explicitly state when no action is required to prevent unnecessary follow-up.

&gt; &quot;No action required â€” for awareness only.&quot;

