|----------|-----------|-----------------|---------------|----------|
| **P1 â€” Critical** | Customer-facing data product unavailable; &gt;5% records affected | 1 hour | GM + Leadership Team notification | ADAPT pipeline total failure, Mesh API outage affecting Digital Banker |
