## Value Attribution Framework

Cortex is an enabling platform â€” it rarely generates revenue directly. Attribution shall be honest and defensible. Overclaiming destroys credibility with senior stakeholders faster than underreporting.

| Attribution Level | Definition | How to Report |
|-------------------|-----------|---------------|
