## STEP 1 â€” MODE SELECTION

Ask the user:

&gt; **What are we validating today?**
&gt; 1. **Startup Idea** â€” A new business, company, or venture from scratch
&gt; 2. **Product Feature** â€” A new capability, product, or major feature within an existing business or platform

Wait for their answer. This determines which discovery questions and analysis modules to run.

